{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Meeting_with_the_Minister_of_State",
  "title": "A Meeting with the Minister of State",
  "summary": "At the New Republic Embassy in Plaxton City, recently reinstated Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard meets with Cordelia Nivhya, the shrewd, patriotic Minister of State of the Caspian Democratic Union. Ambrosia warns that the Empire intends to hold the CDU responsible for its arms manufacturers supplying New Republic weaponry, framing the trade as a matter of freedom while the Empire casts it as complicity in crimes. Cordelia pushes back sharply, questioning whether the Republic truly owns the galaxy and whether its fleet would actually defend Caspar against an Imperial invasion rather than leave its own protectorates exposed. Ambrosia counsels the CDU to prepare for defense and refuse to be cowed, offering to expose the Empire's history of abusive 'documentation' of its subjects -- including her own and her mother's records -- as a propaganda counter. The two diplomats part on cautiously respectful terms, each aware the Caspian people's will, when faced with the choice between tyranny and safety, may prove decisive, and agreeing they will likely work together again soon.",
